		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="429" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">两个深海龙蜥面对面用尾部架阵，从阵中发射总计34枚的冰刺与雷针，不论冰与雷，都造成对应元素的<span color="#bfdfff">20%,10%,5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">唳霜或啸霆蓄力发射一枚带刺冰球，造成对应元素的<span color="#bfdfff">5%</span><span>伤害，并扣除角色</span><span color="#72ff72">30点</span><span>能量，若能量不足则无视护盾额外扣除一定比例的生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">唳霜后撤一步。随后向前翻滚，用尾部扫两圈，造成两段<span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">啸霆使用尾部产生雷球，雷球破裂产生3个雷刺，造成<span color="#ffacff">30%,15%,7.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="927" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">啸霆将尾部插入地面，在一定区域内不断生成雷棘，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%,30%,15%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">唳霜后撤一步。先用右爪扫，造成<span color="#b9b9b9">30%</span><span>伤害，再用左爪扫，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>伤害，最后双爪敲，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1151" width="441" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfff">(强化)<span color="#ffffff">当某个龙蜥濒死时，另一种龙蜥将在10s后回复其</span><span color="#ffdfbf">50%</span><span color="#ffffff">的生命值使其重新加入战斗。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="436" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当某个龙蜥濒死时，两只龙蜥跳到场地中央，缠绕尾部，产生超导场持续造成<span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>+</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，随后两只龙蜥均发射对应的激光，造成对应元素的</span><span color="#bfdfff">100%,50%,<br/>25%,10%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">两个深海龙蜥爬上中央的<span textDecoration="underline">糙岩石柱</span><span>，不断朝玩家发射涤魔子弹，都造成对应元素的</span><span color="#bfdfff">5%</span><span>伤害并扣除角色</span><span color="#72ff72">30点</span><span>能量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
