			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">糙岩石柱：<span color="#ffe599">8岩</span><span>盾，受到近战攻击-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.08岩</span><span>，击破可击落位于其上的吞雷。</span></p>
